description: Fabulous renovated 2 bed 2 bath unit in City Point, with hardware floor throughout, central AC, lots of lights thru the windows and skylight. Walk upstairs to a spacious living room and the large open kitchen with the massive center island. Stylish bathroom with beautiful tile floor and steam shower for your guests. Main bedroom has spacious shower and exposed brick wall. Second bedroom also has large closet with lots of configuration possibility. Walk past the laundry area to your private roof deck with views of beach. One year limited builder's warranty is included, condo fee is estimated subject to changes due to seller's ability to control cost, and large basement storage room is included. Short distance to Seaport and downtown Boston, Route 93 and 90 highway access within 10 minutes. Come and check out this newly renovated unit today!
